      "blocks": {
        "question_RG4Rpp": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "1. Why does Jasion partner with Totwoo?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Freedom means more when it’s shared. Jasion encourages people to explore the world with confidence and independence, while Totwoo helps loved ones stay emotionally connected — no matter the distance. By bringing together electric mobility and smart jewelry, we combine movement with meaning. Together, we share a vision of a lifestyle that values freedom, connection, and moments that truly matter.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_9YNTGi": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "2. How can Jasion eBikes and Totwoo enhance your riding experience?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Jasion and Totwoo create a seamless blend of mobility and emotional connection. While Jasion eBikes provide power, comfort, and flexibility for commuting, weekend rides, or outdoor adventures, Totwoo keeps you connected with loved ones through a simple touch — no matter the distance. Together, they turn every ride into a meaningful journey, adding warmth and connection to every mile.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_WJmtKJ": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "3. Where can I purchase the spring campaign bundles and get the latest information?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>The exclusive spring bundles are available on the official Jasion and Totwoo websites, featuring special limited-time offers. For the latest updates, promotions, and campaign details, follow Jasion and Totwoo on social media (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/321883149636188/\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/321883149636188/\">Facebook</a>,<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jasionbike/\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/jasionbike/\"> Instagram</a>, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@JasionBike\" title=\"https://www.youtube.com/@JasionBike\">YouTube</a>) and join our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/321883149636188/\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/321883149636188/\">community groups</a> to stay connected.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_eQYbgX": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "4. What is the warranty policy and when will the products be shipped?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Jasion and Totwoo products are covered under their respective official warranty policies. For detailed warranty coverage and terms, please visit each brand’s official website.</p><p>Jasion orders typically take 1–2 business days to process before shipment. Please note that processing times may be extended during peak sales periods. Once your order has shipped, you will receive a confirmation email with tracking details.</p><p>Standard delivery usually takes 5–7 business days, depending on your location. Please note that the delivery dates provided are estimates only, and actual delivery times may vary.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
